192
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:38,670
- Come here. - Keep your greasy paws off me.
- 來吧 - 不要用你的髒手碰我

193
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:41,430
Wish me luck, momma.
祝我好運 媽媽

194
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,410
Good luck.
祝你好運

195
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:21,380
Next.
下一個

196
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:22,800
Grab a seat.
坐吧

197
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:24,870
You've ever given blood before?
您之前獻過血嗎

198
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:26,340
Yes, ma'am. I have.
獻過 女士

199
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:30,810
You're the belt man.
你是那個皮帶男孩

200
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:32,440
Desmond, yes, ma'am.
我叫戴斯蒙德 是的 女士

201
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:35,500
Well, Desmond, we can't take your blood two days in a row.
戴斯蒙德 你不能連著兩天來獻血

202
00:15:35,530 --> 00:15:37,600
Well, that's good. I came to get mine back.
那好吧 我來是為了要回我的血

203
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:38,680
You what?
什麼

204
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:40,250
My blood, I need it back.
我的血 把它還給我

205
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,800
Well, it don't work like that.
那樣可不行

206
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:44,260
We can't just give it back to you.
我們不能還給你

207
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:45,790
Well, you got to.
你必須還給我

208
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:48,020
Ever since you stuck me with that needle,
自從你用針頭紮了我之後

209
00:15:48,050 --> 00:15:49,840
my heart has been beating real fast.
我的心就跳得飛快

210
00:15:50,130 --> 00:15:52,750
Everytime I think about you, it beats faster still.
每次我想到你 就跳得更快了

211
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:56,400
I never heard that one before.
我從沒聽過這樣的搭訕

212
00:15:56,430 --> 00:15:57,700
It's pretty corny.
陳腔濫調

213
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:58,810
It is?
是嗎

214
00:15:59,310 --> 00:15:59,810
Yeah.
沒錯

215
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:02,760
That's a shame. I've done practicing that all night.
真可惜 我還練了整整一個晚上

216
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,750
No good?
表現得不好嗎

217
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,840
I didn't say that.
我可沒那麼說

218
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:31,330
What's the difference between an artery and a vein?
動脈和靜脈的區別是什麼

219
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,850
What are you talking about?
你在說什麼

220
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,580
The boy's accident.
那個男孩的事故

221
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,830
Arteries spurt blood.
動脈的血是噴出來的

222
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:43,350
And veins?
靜脈呢

223
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,200
Bleed.
流出來的

224
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:50,580
I think you need to practice your
我覺得 你應該在出門前

225
00:16:50,610 --> 00:16:53,350
boy-girl-dating-talk at home before you come out.
好好練習下 如何和女生聊天

226
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,280
Yeah, I probably do.
沒錯 我確實需要練習

227
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:59,880
I'll give you a book if you're that interested.
如果你感興趣 我可以給你一本書

228
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,290
On dating?
關於約會的嗎

229
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,260
On blood.
關於血液的

230
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:15,960
Another medical question perhaps?
還有什麼醫學問題嗎

231
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:20,200
No. I just think you're the prettiest thing I've ever seen.
不 我覺得 你是我見過最漂亮的姑娘

232
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:23,580
That's because I'm sitting in the dark.
因為我坐在暗處 你看不清楚

233
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:27,020
No.
不

234
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:30,430
You're just beautiful.
你真是太美了

235
00:17:55,370 --> 00:17:57,230
Out of the way!
別擋道

236
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:01,100
You need to watch where you're going.
你走路得看著前面

237
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:15,210
I'm sorry. I didn't think you'd mind.
抱歉 我以為你不介意

238
00:18:15,670 --> 00:18:17,000
You didn't ask.
你又沒問

239
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:19,640
I thought you might've liked it.
我以為你會接受

240
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:21,720
Well, I might've if you'd asked.
你要是問了 我說不定會接受

241
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,500
You coming?
你要來嗎

242
00:18:36,260 --> 00:18:38,120
Watch where you're walking!
走路看著點

243
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:01,190
Why didn't you say nothing to us?
為何你之前沒告訴我們

244
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:02,970
'Cause you would've tried and talked me out of it.
因為你們會盡力勸我不要去

245
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,500
I know what I'm doing is right.
而我知道自己這樣做才是對的

246
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:06,590
And what about His commandment?
那聖經上說的十誡呢

247
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,240
It's not killing in a war.
在戰爭中 殺戮不是罪惡

248
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:11,390
I was protecting loads of boys from our church from going.
我是在幫助我們教堂裏的小伙子們 以免他們參戰

249
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:11,890
Yeah.
好吧

250
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:14,240
There's a war and they need men.
現在是戰時 國家需要兵源

251
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:17,470
And working in a paper mill ain't going to save this country.
在造紙廠工作 並不會拯救這個國家

252
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:27,760
Looks like a movie star,
你看起來像個電影明星

253
00:19:28,890 --> 00:19:29,890
our boy.
小伙子

254
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,860
Nice uniform.
軍服很帥

255
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:36,410
Good hat.
帽子也不錯

256
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,820
Reminds me of how Artie Giddens looked
讓我想起 我們出征法國時

257
00:19:40,850 --> 00:19:43,260
in his look in his uniform when we went to France.
亞提·吉登斯穿著那套軍服的樣子

258
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,370
Remember him, Bertha?
還記得他嗎 貝莎

259
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:46,950
Don't, Tom.
別這樣 湯姆

260
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:47,980
What?
怎麼了

261
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:53,600
I'm just saying how snappy Artie looked in his uniform.
我只是想說 亞提裝著軍服真是精神

262
00:19:54,780 --> 00:19:57,000
All you girls certainly seemed to think so.
你們這些姑娘貌似都這麼覺得

263
00:19:57,300 --> 00:20:00,560
He had them flocking to him. He was most proud.
當時 他身邊圍的全是姑娘 他可驕傲了

264
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:07,780
I just hope that when our Hal get shot,
我只希望 如果哈爾中彈

265
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:09,640
it's through the front of his jacket.
子彈會從他夾克的前面穿過

266
00:20:10,820 --> 00:20:13,590
Like a simple entry wound, not much mess.
那種乾脆的射入傷 不會弄得太難看

267
00:20:14,090 --> 00:20:16,430
Artie got hit in the back, It blew most of his
當初亞提是從背後被擊中

268
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:20,570
guts and intestines out his front, awful everywhere.
內臟和腸子全從前面炸了出來 掉得滿地都是

269
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,860
Wrecked his uniform entirely.
完全把他的制服毀了

270
00:20:28,930 --> 00:20:30,280
It was lucky he was dead
幸好他當時已經死了

271
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:34,540
so he never knew how awful his uniform looked.
永遠不會知道 他的軍服有多難看

272
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:40,550
Get out of my sight.
你給我滾出去

273
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:41,450
What are you? Part mountain goat?
你到底是誰呀 難道是山羊嗎

274
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:45,530
Are you gonna help me, Desmond Doss?
你還要不要幫我一把啊 戴斯蒙德·道斯

275
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:48,120
Or are you just gonna leave me stranded?
還是就這麼丟下我 困在這裏

276
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:52,910
I'll help you.
我來幫你

277
00:21:52,970 --> 00:21:54,500
But it's gonna cost you.
但你要答應一個條件

278
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:55,700
What?
什麼條件

279
00:21:56,450 --> 00:21:57,400
A kiss.
一個吻

280
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,560
That is pure blackmail.
這簡直就是赤裸裸的敲詐

281
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:02,860
Well yes, ma'am it is,
是的 女士 沒錯

282
00:22:02,890 --> 00:22:04,800
but that is still my condition.
不過我依然堅持我的要求

283
00:22:07,220 --> 00:22:08,540
That's the deal.
那就說定了

284
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:11,510
And I'm going to hold you to it.
我會把你帶上去

285
00:22:24,690 --> 00:22:25,690
Well, hold on now.
等等

286
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,430
You ain't gonna slap me, are you?
你不會再扇我耳光了吧

287
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:32,970
'Cause I'll fall off, I'm gonna take you with me.
因為要是我跌下去 我會把你也拽下去的

288
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:35,490
Kiss me and find out.
那就吻我試試看吧

289
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:25,350
What?
怎麼了

290
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:28,300
I have to enlist.
我必須去參軍了

291
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:32,710
I can't stay here while all them go fight for me.
我不能待在後方 讓他們為我拚命

292
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:33,570
Yes, you can.
你可以的

293
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:35,270
- You can stay here. - Dorothy, I have to.
- 你可以待在這裏 - 多蘿西 我必須去

294
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:36,690
I want to be a medic.
我想去做醫護兵

295
00:23:36,970 --> 00:23:39,580
I figure I'll be saving people, not killing them.
我覺得我可以去救人 而不是去殺人

296
00:23:43,490 --> 00:23:45,510
I have to go to work. I'm going to be late.
我得去上班了 我快要遲到了

297
00:23:49,900 --> 00:23:50,960
Dorothy, darling.
多蘿西 親愛的

298
00:23:50,980 --> 00:23:52,210
Dorothy. Dorothy.
多蘿西 多蘿西

299
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:58,370
So are you gonna ask me to marry you or what?
所以你是要向我求婚 還是怎麼呢

300
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,910
Well, I don't know. You're still going to have me?
我不知道啊 你會答應我嗎

301
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:05,190
Well, I wouldn't know, you haven't asked.
我也不知道 你還沒問呢

302
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:07,320
Well, I'm asking you,
那我這就求婚

303
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:10,090
with all my heart and then some.
真心誠意

304
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:11,270
Will you marry me?
你願意嫁給我嗎

305
00:24:11,570 --> 00:24:12,790
Then, yes.
那我就答應吧

306
00:24:13,190 --> 00:24:14,480
Yes. I will.
我願意

307
00:24:24,150 --> 00:24:24,880
When?
什麼時候呢

308
00:24:25,290 --> 00:24:27,000
Soon as you get your first leave.
等到你第一次休假回家 我們就結婚

309
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:29,020
But I still don't like you at this moment.
不過現在 我還是不喜歡你

310
00:24:29,430 --> 00:24:30,260
Yeah.
好吧

311
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:31,470
Okay.
好吧

312
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:33,980
Okay. Well, I love you.
我愛你

313
00:24:34,050 --> 00:24:35,050
Shhhh.
噓

314
00:24:47,290 --> 00:24:49,490
Momma said come see you here.
媽媽說 在這裏可以找到你

315
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,680
These three were my best friends.
當初 他們三個是我最好的朋友

316
00:24:58,290 --> 00:24:59,620
I grew up with 'em.
我和他們一起長大

317
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:03,440
I got into trouble with 'em. Chased girls with 'em.
和他們一起闖禍 和他們一起追女孩

318
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,400
And I enlisted with 'em.
然後也和他們一起入伍

319
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,350
Now my friends are there,
現在 我的朋友們就在這裏

320
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:14,560
covered in dirt and grasss, and eaten by worms.
被泥土和野草覆蓋 被蟲子吞噬

321
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:19,930
I don't want to have to visit my sons here.
我不想也來這裏祭奠我的兒子們

322
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:23,480
Daddy, I... I signed up already.
爸爸 我已經報名了

323
00:25:26,250 --> 00:25:28,450
I couldn't do otherwise, pop.
我別無選擇啊 老爹

324
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:33,120
- Everybody else is doing...- You ain't everybody else!
- 其他人都... - 你不是其他人

325
00:25:35,130 --> 00:25:37,360
Everybody else jumps in and does thing quick,
其他人都不加思考

326
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:38,020
without thinking!
魯莽行事

327
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:41,080
Like the damn idiot fools we were.
就像我們當初那樣 都是白癡

328
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:43,250
You know what? Soldiers who live,
你要明白 那些能活下來的士兵

329
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:44,600
they live cause they can do that!
是因為他們有能力活下來

330
00:25:44,630 --> 00:25:45,630
You can't!
而你不行

331
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:47,540
Look, you gotta sit
你得冷靜下來

332
00:25:47,570 --> 00:25:49,340
and think and pray about everything.
好好思考 好好祈禱

333
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:53,300
I mean, look at you, you're doing it right now
瞧瞧你 你現在就做得很好

334
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:55,840
You won't be able to live with yourself if you go.
如果你去了 你根本就活不下去

335
00:25:55,870 --> 00:25:57,940
No, I won't be able to live with myself if I don't.
不 如果我不去 我才活不下去

336
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,290
I'm going to be a medic.
我要去當醫護兵

337
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:01,920
That's going to be my way to serve.
我要以這種方式服役

338
00:26:01,950 --> 00:26:04,160
See, there you go, thinking it all out.
看來你都想明白了啊

339
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:07,990
What, you figure this war is going to fit in with you?
怎麼著 你覺得這場戰爭會配合你嗎

340
00:26:08,090 --> 00:26:09,090
Your ideas?
配合你的想法嗎

341
00:26:10,260 --> 00:26:12,870
Well, I don't doubt it's going to be hard.
我毫不懷疑 這肯定會非常艱難

342
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:16,880
It won't be hard. It will be impossible.
不是艱難 而是根本就不可能

343
00:26:17,740 --> 00:26:18,710
You know, whatever
你知道嗎

344
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,400
beliefs you have in your crazy head now,
不管你那瘋狂的腦子裏 現在有什麼想法

345
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:22,520
they won't ever play out it.
戰爭都不會按你想的發展

346
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:24,080
It don't work that way.
戰爭從來都不是那樣的

347
00:26:24,770 --> 00:26:26,160
And if by some, I don't know,
如果真有奇跡出現

348
00:26:26,180 --> 00:26:27,900
miracle chance you survive,
你能活下來

349
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:30,450
you won't be giving no thanks to God.
你也應該感謝上帝

350
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:36,300
- Ready? - Ready.
- 準備好了嗎 - 好了

351
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:37,240
We all need some air.
我們需要新鮮空氣

352
00:26:37,260 --> 00:26:39,530
C'mon fellas, shake a leg. Uncle Sam's got you now.
來吧 夥計們 快點吧 為國效力吧

353
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:40,810
Say goodbye to Momma.
跟媽媽說再見吧

354
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:42,630
C'mon.
快點啊

355
00:26:43,340 --> 00:26:45,300
Ladies, please! Step away from the bus.
女士們 請遠離大巴

356
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:46,370
I almost forgot.
我差點忘了

357
00:26:46,490 --> 00:26:47,450
Do I need a crowbar?
我需要把撬棍 才能把你們分開嗎

358
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,120
Here.
給你

359
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:50,650
I want you to have this.
我想要你帶上這個

360
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:52,120
It's mine.
這是我的

361
00:26:54,170 --> 00:26:55,550
You keep it right here,
你隨身帶著它

362
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:57,500
where I'll be.
就像我也在你身旁

363
00:26:59,980 --> 00:27:00,600
Bye.
再見

364
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,640
I love you.
我愛你

365
00:27:47,530 --> 00:27:48,930
Hey, don't say that about my girl.
不許那樣說我女人

366
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:52,370
Hey. Sorry, pal.
不好意思 兄弟

367
00:27:53,370 --> 00:27:55,040
Means you're the person.
這意味著 你就是那個傢伙

368
00:27:56,250 --> 00:27:57,530
I got a punch here.
我這裏挨了一拳

369
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:59,430
Nah, it's just a bump.
不 只是被撞了下

370
00:27:59,930 --> 00:28:01,620
Do I have to gaze at your deformity
難不成我每次走向自己的床位

371
00:28:01,650 --> 00:28:03,110
everytime I walk to my bed?
還要盯著你那玩意看嗎

372
00:28:03,130 --> 00:28:05,500
Gaze upon it in envy, my friend.
